Stable Release: DIALS 2.0
=========================

The current stable release can be downloaded from `Github <https://github.com/dials/dials/releases/latest>`_,
where you can also find further `release notes <https://github.com/dials/dials/releases/latest>`_.

.. button::
   :text: DIALS 2.0.4 Linux installer
   :link: https://github.com/dials/dials/releases/download/v2.0.0/dials-v2-0-4-linux-x86_64.tar.xz

.. button::
   :text: DIALS 2.0.4 Linux installer (Python 3 preview, unsupported)
   :link: https://github.com/dials/dials/releases/download/v2.0.0/dials-v2-0-4-linux-x86_64-conda3.tar.xz

.. button::
   :text: DIALS 2.0.4 Mac installer
   :link: https://github.com/dials/dials/releases/download/v2.0.0/dials-v2-0-4-macosx.pkg

.. button::
   :text: DIALS 2.0.2 Mac installer (OS X 10.6)
   :link: https://github.com/dials/dials/releases/download/v2.0.0/dials-v2-0-2-macosx-10.6.pkg

.. button::
   :text: DIALS 2.0.4 Mac tar archive
   :link: https://github.com/dials/dials/releases/download/v2.0.0/dials-v2-0-4-macosx.tar.gz

.. button::
   :text: DIALS 2.0.2 Mac tar archive (OS X 10.6)
   :link: https://github.com/dials/dials/releases/download/v2.0.0/dials-v2-0-2-macosx-10.6.tar.gz

.. button::
   :text: DIALS 2.0.4 Source installer
   :link: https://github.com/dials/dials/releases/download/v2.0.0/dials-v2-0-4-source.tar.xz

Stable Release: DIALS 1.14
==========================

We still support the previous stable release version of DIALS. This can be downloaded
from `Github`__,
where you can also find further `release notes`__.

.. __: https://github.com/dials/dials/releases/tag/v1.14.0
__ https://github.com/dials/dials/releases/tag/v1.14.0

